  "original_title": "22 \u0b86\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0baf\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc7 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Only 22,000 tourists are currently staying in the country",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Sri Lanka Tourism Development Authority, there are currently 22,000 foreign tourists staying in the country.",
        "According to the Tourism Development Authority, tourists have visited 136 countries.",
        "Of these, 1,785 were from Australia, 2,295 from Canada, 1,310 from France, 1,883 from Germany, 2,569 from India, 1,392 from Russia, 2,397 from the UK and 1,379 from the United States.",
        "It has also been informed that steps are being taken in collaboration with industry partners to explore the needs of tourists in Sri Lanka and facilitate them.",
        "The Tourism Development Authority further said that all efforts have been made to reduce the inconvenience caused to tourists due to the current crisis."
      ],
